    <div data-cid="1085292">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1085292">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1182787/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u1182787-1.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1182787/" class="name">拔刀诀</a>

            <span class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>

        <span content="2006-10-27" class="main-meta">2006-10-27 16:05:05</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1085292/">一堂小资语文课</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1085292_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1085292">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        前些日子在卓越网订书时，顺道捎上了安意如的《当时只道是寻常》，因见网上不少书评津津乐道，不由起了好奇之心。 夜半失眠，想找点短文培养睡意，在一堆新书中随手拎起这本。 对古典诗词，我素来喜欢但不是十分的热爱，往往在看小说和其他文章时偶尔得窥一斑，惊艳之下，才去...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1085292-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1085292_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1085292_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1085292" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1085292">
                                77
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="1085292" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-1085292">
